<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cmn-Hans">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../style/miyun.min.css" media="screen" title="no title">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../style/weui.min.css">
    <title>查看问题答案</title>
</head>
<body class="body">
    <div class="component-title">问题</div>
    <div class="ask-body">
        <p class="question-detail" id="question">
            怀孕5个月， 腰酸背痛，是什么原因？
       
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="component-title">答案</div>
    <div class="ask-body">
        <p class="question-detail" id="answer">
            你好， 我是某某医院,孕期腰背痛你好， 我是某某医院,孕期腰背痛你好， 我是某某医院,孕期腰背痛你好， 我是某某医院,孕期腰背痛
       
        </p>
    </div>
    <p class="weui-cells__title">查看图片</p>
    <div class="weui-cells weui-cells_form" id="uploaderCustom">
        <div class="weui-cell">
            <div class="weui-cell__bd">
                <div class="weui-uploader">
                    <div class="weui-uploader__bd" id="shotcutview">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ask-btn-area">
        <a  class="ask-btn-primary" id="onemore" disable="false">追问 ￥0</a>
    </div>
    <div class="ask-btn-area">
        <a href="#" class="ask-btn-primary" onclick="like()">点赞！医生棒棒哒！</a>
    </div>
    <div id="free-tag">
        <p class="free-tag">您有一次免费追问机会</p>
    </div>

    <script src="../js/jquery-2.1.4.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/api.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/weui.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $.ajax({
                "url": "../../Services/MedicalCare.ashx?action=getanswer",
                "type": "POST",
                "dataType": "json",
                "data": {
                    "code": getUrlParam("code"),
                    "QueId": getUrlParam("QueId")
                },
                "success": function (questionInfo) {
                    $("#question").html("");
                    $("#question").append(questionInfo[0].queDetail);
                    $("#answer").html("");
                    $("#answer").append(questionInfo[0].ansDetail);
                    var dutViewInnerHtml = " <ul class=\"weui-uploader__files\" id=\"uploaderCustomFiles\">";
                    for (var i = 0; i < questionInfo[0].imageUrls.length; i++) {
                        dutViewInnerHtml = dutViewInnerHtml + " <li class=\"weui-uploader__file\" data-id=\"" + i + "\" style=\"background-image: url('" + questionInfo[0].imageUrls[i] + "');\"></li>";
                    }
                    document.getElementById("shotcutview").innerHTML = dutViewInnerHtml + "</ul>";


                    $.ajax({
                        url: "../../Services/MedicalCare.ashx?action=hasreasked",
                        dataType: "html",
                        type: 'post',
                        data: {
                            QueId: questionInfo[0].queId,
                        },
                        success: function (hJson) {
                            if (hJson == "0") {
                                $.ajax({
                                    url: "../../Services/MedicalCare.ashx?action=getprice",
                                    dataType: "html",
                                    type: 'post',
                                    data: {
                                        ProductType: "1001",
                                        AddtionKey: "QUESTION",
                                        AddtionValue: questionInfo[0].queId,
                                    },
                                    success: function (hJson) {
                                        if (hJson != "0") {
                                            document.getElementById("onemore").text = '追问 ￥0.99'; 
                                        }
                                    }
                                });
                                document.getElementById("onemore").href = "https://open.weixin.qq.com/connect/oauth2/authorize?appid=wx2500d73cdacd7fa6&redirect_uri=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bestmiyun.com%2Fmiyun%2Fpatient%2Fswitch-doctor-to-ask.html%3ffatherQueID%3d" + questionInfo[0].queId + "%26ProductType%3d1001&response_type=code&scope=snsapi_base&state=123#wechat_redirect";

                            }
                            else
                            {
                                document.getElementById("onemore").text = '已追问';
                            }
                        }
                    });


                   

                    


                    

                    if (!questionInfo.askOneMore) {
                        $("#onemore").attr('disable', 'true');
                        $("free-tag").empty();
                    }

                    document.querySelector('#uploaderCustomFiles').addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                        var target = e.target;
                        while (!target.classList.contains('weui-uploader__file') && target) {
                            target = target.parentNode;
                        }
                        if (!target) return;
                        var url = target.getAttribute('style') || '';
                        var id = target.getAttribute('data-id'); 
                        if (url) {
                            url = url.match(/url\((.*?)\)/)[1];
                            var gallery = weui.gallery(url);
                        }
                        
                    });
                },
                "error": function () {
                }
            });
        });
    </script> 
</body>
</html>
